application_type_full: Outline planning permission: Some matters reserved
description: Outline application: mixed-use development of former railway lands. Development comprises business and employment uses within the B1 use class; C3 uses (inc student accommodation), serviced apartments and hotels; services within the A1, A2, A3, A4 and A5 use classes; community, health, education, cultural, assembly and leisure facilities, within D1 and D2; night clubs; multi storey and other car parking; re-erection of the linked triplet of gas holder guide frames to enclose new residential and other development, on the site of the Western Goods Shed; re-erection of the guide frame for gas holder number 8, alongside the re-erected triplet, to enclose new play facilities and open space; works of alteration to other existing buildings and structures, new streets and other means of access and circulation; landscaping including open space; new bridge crossings and other works along the Regent's Canal;  and other infrastructure works and facilities.
